235 likes, 11 comments - tennis_magazine_ on February 29, 2020: "#didyouknow

Throwback to 2008..Ana Ivanovic and Jelena Jankovic, who were big rivals in those days played a grand slam semifinal against each other - French Open.The winner will fight for first grand slam title and will be number 1.Ana Ivanovic won in 3-setter with 6-4 3-6 6-4 and later won her first grand slam title.She was first wta star from Serbia to win grand slam (except Monica Seles) and reach number 1.Jelena Jankovic reached number 1 later in that year and 2008 was a year of history in Serbian tennis.
